*** '''Kolodion:''' I've made a note of the spells you still need to learn in your journal.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If player doesn't have 75 Magic:}}
*** '''Kolodion:''' You have indeed shown potential, [player name].
*** '''Kolodion:''' However, a wizard of your level wouldn't stand a chance.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If player has mastered all the god spells and is 75 Magic:}}
*** '''Kolodion:''' I am one of the most powerful mages in existence. But even my power has limitations. There are some beings however that have power exceeding even my own.
*** '''Kolodion:''' I have detected three life forces within the Wilderness, each of them giving out a strange magical power, one unlike any I have ever felt before.
*** '''Kolodion:''' If we could harness the power of these beings, I could imbue your god cape with that power, greatly increasing its potential.
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
